/* ==UserStyle==
@name           Google Darkest Fusion 1/2
@namespace      USO Archive
@author         Atx
@description    `Do you like my style? Please support my work and fund me a coffee (via PayPal to the left of "Install" button). Also share style with your friends. Thank you for being awesome!Darkest Fusion supports almost every Google site. Due to a style size limit Darkest Fusion has been divided into 2 parts. That one contains dark theme for most common used Google sites: <strong>About, Account management, Admin, Alerts, Books, Calendar, Contacts, Drive, Finance, Hangouts, Maps, My Activity, One, Patents, Payments, Passwords, Photos, Scholar, Search, Sheets, Tasks, Translate, Travel and Trends</strong>.<strong><mark>Second style is available >>> <a href="https://userstyles.org/styles/180430/google-darkest-fusion-2-2">there</a> <<<</mark></strong>Keep and Support currently have stock dark themes.Originally based on great work by DeathTBO who abandoned his project so I decided to continue his work by rebuilting everything from scratch. I hope you like my vision for Dark Google :)`
@version        20210419.17.3
@license        NO-REDISTRIBUTION
@preprocessor   uso
@advanced dropdown logo_google "Google logo color" {
	default_logo "Default*" <<<EOT /*test1*\/ EOT;
nododdle_logo "Default (No Doodle)" <<<EOT /*test2*\/
.k1zIA.rSk4se
{
	background: url("https://www.google.com/images/branding/googlelogo/2x/googlelogo_color_272x92dp.png") no-repeat center !important;
background-size: auto;
	background-size: 272px 92px !important;
	height: 100% !important;
	width: 100% !important;
}

