sourceCode:
/* ==UserStyle==
@name           ParanoidGram
@namespace      USO Archive
@author         Verticablets
@description    `Update: get the user.css file (a better way to install this theme) at: <a href="https://github.com/Verticablets/ParanoidGram">My Github</a>A customizable dark Instagram theme with a few animations and effects.Right click is enabled in posts and stories.You can change every colour inside the theme.Feel free to suggest changes/give feedback.<a href="https://app.singlelink.co/u/Verticablets">My Social Media</a>To use a background image, send the image you want to use as the background to a contact on Instagram or use the picture of an Instagram post. right click > open image in new tab and copy the link to that image. you can paste that link in the field "Enter URL" once you click "customize settings" If you upload the image it won't work, it has to be the method above.`
@version        20210127.1.52
@license        NO-REDISTRIBUTION
@preprocessor   uso
@advanced dropdown https-null "Background Image" {
https-null "Default*" <<<EOT https:null EOT;

